name: Qr04_Extracao_Base_Prospect_Offline_Telefone_SemOTC_Algar
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
  'TCBB' AS COD_PARCEIRO,
  CPF,
   '' AS CNPJ,
  DDD_01 AS DDD,
  TEL_01 AS TELEFONE
FROM
  TB_BASE_PROSPECT_SEMOTC_FILTRADA_ALGAR
WHERE
    LEN(TEL_01) >= 8
AND LEN(DDD_01) = 2
UNION ALL
